Title: 009: Neuroscience, Machine Learning and Moore’s Law with Muhsin Karim, Phd
Description:
In this session of the Super Data Science Podcast, I chat with Neuroscience PhD Turned Retail Data Analyst Muhsin Karim. You will know what is neuroscience, learn more about machine learning and discover some surprising implications from Moore’s Law.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at https://www.superdatascience.com/9
